==Doubts as for date==
It does not seem possible, that she was laid down in January 1898 and launched on 6 July the same year. One Russian book says she was laid down on 6 January 1897 ((''А.С. Александров, С.А. Балакин'': „Асама” и другие. Японские броненосные крейсера программы 1895-1896г.''), series Morskaya Kampania 1/2006  [[User:Pibwl|Pibwl]] [[User_talk:Pibwl|&larr;&laquo;]] 00:31, 7 December 2007 (UTC)
: You are correct - there was a typo on the date, which is now fixed. --[[User:MChew|MChew]] ([[User talk:MChew|talk]]) 06:54, 7 December 2007 (UTC)
